Dear Santa...

Dear Santa,

This year I've been busy!

Last Thursday I pushed in the mud (-17 points). In July I gave a wet willie, then I took it back (-5 points). Last Tuesday I gave a Dutch Oven (-10 points). Last month I gave a life-saving blood transfusion (50 points). In September I ruled Iran as a cruel and heartless dictator (-700 points).

Overall, I've been naughty (-682 points). For Christmas I deserve a spanking!

Sincerely,
crazywildgirl
